327
00:21:34,807 --> 00:21:36,206
Get aboard.

328
00:22:03,769 --> 00:22:06,203
Well, gentlemen, this is it.

329
00:22:06,271 --> 00:22:09,206
Exact replica
of the P.O.W. camp.

330
00:22:09,308 --> 00:22:10,707
Who built it?

331
