339
00:22:50,849 --> 00:22:52,282
Good evening.

340
00:22:52,351 --> 00:22:54,285
Hi. How are you?

341
00:22:54,353 --> 00:22:58,289
Mr. Ky, you can serve
when you're ready.

342
00:23:00,292 --> 00:23:01,691
Good evening.

343
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:03,193
As you were.

344
00:23:03,262 --> 00:23:07,366
