346
00:23:08,434 --> 00:23:09,992
This is Kevin Scott.

347
00:23:10,102 --> 00:23:13,367
He's well-trained in weapons
and training techniques.

348
00:23:13,472 --> 00:23:15,702
And this is Mr. Ky.

349
00:23:15,774 --> 00:23:19,540
We'll be eating Vietnamese food
from now on.

350
00:23:19,611 --> 00:23:23,206
We don't want
to smell like Americans.

351
00:23:23,282 --> 00:23:25,216
Any questions?

352
00:23:26,785 --> 00:23:28,013
Good.

353
00:23:28,087 --> 00:23:30,715
How long were you there?

354
00:23:30,789 --> 00:23:32,222
I wasn't.

355
00:23:32,291 --> 00:23:33,724
Too young.

356
00:23:35,260 --> 00:23:37,524
Is he going with us?

357
00:23:37,596 --> 00:23:40,690
Served in
Fourth Recon Marines.

358
00:23:40,766 --> 00:23:42,529
Served?

359
00:23:42,601 --> 00:23:46,560
I was discharged
for striking a radio operator

360
00:23:46,638 --> 00:23:49,573
who fell asleep
at his post.

361
00:23:54,246 --> 00:23:58,239
You're worried that I have
no combat experience.

362
00:23:58,317 --> 00:23:59,750
You're right.

363
00:23:59,818 --> 00:24:04,687
