Fuckin' pimp!

415
00:27:11,109 --> 00:27:13,077
Go! Go! Go!

416
00:27:13,178 --> 00:27:15,043
Blaster, go!
Come on, baby, go!

417
00:27:19,151 --> 00:27:21,176
O.K. Come on, man.

418
00:27:22,654 --> 00:27:24,178
Take it home!

419
00:27:25,257 --> 00:27:26,849
Come on, Scott.

420
00:27:26,892 --> 00:27:29,486
Go! Go, Sailor, go!

421
00:27:29,561 --> 00:27:31,153
Come on, rookie!

422
00:27:31,229 --> 00:27:33,163
All right, come on!

423
00:27:33,231 --> 00:27:34,721
Go! Go, Sailor!

424
00:27:37,269 --> 00:27:38,702
Hit it!

425
00:27:48,780 --> 00:27:50,714
What are you doing?

426
00:27:53,285 --> 00:27:56,152
You don't ever quit, boy.

427
00:27:56,221 --> 00:27:58,416
Not when it's for real.

428
00:28:00,025 --> 00:28:01,390
All right. That's enough.

429
00:28:05,697 --> 00:28:06,959
Shit!

430
00:28:07,032 --> 00:28:08,124
Damn!

431
00:28:08,200 --> 00:28:10,134
Too much civilian life.

432
00:28:10,235 --> 00:28:11,668
Pull it in!

433
00:28:13,238 --> 00:28:15,172
O.K.! Move your butts!

434
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:16,673
Double time!

435
00:28:21,747 --> 00:28:23,180
Good shooting, Colonel.

436
00:28:23,248 --> 00:28:25,182
Blaster, your elbow down.

437
00:28:25,250 --> 00:28:26,683
Yeah, yeah.

438
00:28:28,253 --> 00:28:29,686
Sailor, stop spraying!

439
00:28:29,755 --> 00:28:31,188
Conserve your ammo!

440
00:28:37,229 --> 00:28:41,165
You haven't got
one in the kill zone!

441
00:28:41,233 --> 00:28:44,168
These hands
were made to fly.

442
00:28:44,269 --> 00:28:48,706
Tell the enemy when
he blows your head off!

443
00:28:48,774 --> 00:28:50,708
Don't lose it, mister!

444
00:28:50,776 --> 00:28:53,074
You kill the enemy,
asshole!

445
00:28:53,145 --> 00:28:55,204
Sailor, I could teach

446
00:28:55,280 --> 00:28:58,716
an undisciplined brawler
like you a lesson.

447
00:28:58,784 --> 00:29:00,649
Make your move, boy.

448
00:29:00,719 --> 00:29:02,653
Scott! A word, please.

449
00:29:06,725 --> 00:29:09,626
Scott, these men
are seasoned veterans.

450
00:29:09,694 --> 00:29:13,130
They can't be treated
like raw recruits.

451
00:29:13,198 --> 00:29:16,133
You have to earn
their respect.

452
00:29:18,236 --> 00:29:19,669
Yes, sir.

453
00:29:51,269 --> 00:29:53,203
Wilkesy's
claustrophobic as shit.

454
00:29:53,271 --> 00:29:57,207
He was the tunnel rat
in our unit.

455
00:29:58,743 --> 00:30:00,176
Goes down a tunnel

456
00:30:00,245 --> 00:30:02,679
to check for
weapon storage.

457
00:30:02,747 --> 00:30:05,682
Turns out there's
somebody down there.

458
00:30:05,750 --> 00:30:09,186
