lashed them against tanks.

513
00:33:10,702 --> 00:33:13,170
For years, I'd wake up

514
00:33:13,238 --> 00:33:16,674
with those frozen faces
staring at me.

515
00:33:19,744 --> 00:33:22,212
Did it ever go away?

516
00:33:23,882 --> 00:33:24,814
No.

517
00:33:27,752 --> 00:33:31,188
