with them though.

518
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:36,790
No.

519
00:33:36,861 --> 00:33:37,793
Left.

520
00:33:37,862 --> 00:33:38,794
No.

521
00:33:38,863 --> 00:33:40,455
Left, right, left.

522
00:33:40,532 --> 00:33:41,965
No.

523
00:33:42,033 --> 00:33:43,466
Get together, guys!

524
00:33:44,536 --> 00:33:45,468
Gentlemen!

525
00:33:45,570 --> 00:33:48,505
The object
of the next exercise--

526
00:33:48,573 --> 00:33:51,508
Get from here
to the bridge

527
00:33:51,576 --> 00:33:53,840
without being tagged
by Wilkes.

528
