Aw, shit. I'm dead.

531
00:34:19,537 --> 00:34:20,970
Wilkesy, I'm supposed--

532
00:34:21,039 --> 00:34:22,097
Shit!

533
00:34:36,054 --> 00:34:37,146
Shit!

