00:35:01,513 --> 00:35:02,844
Fuck, man.

535
00:35:09,521 --> 00:35:10,954
Come on!

536
00:35:12,023 --> 00:35:13,923
Come on. Come on.

537
00:35:13,992 --> 00:35:15,926
You can make it.

538
00:35:15,994 --> 00:35:17,427
Come across.

539
00:35:17,495 --> 00:35:21,431
You people got caught
'cause you got careless.

540
00:35:21,499 --> 00:35:22,932
I told you--

541
00:35:24,502 --> 00:35:25,764
All right, Wilkesy!

542
00:35:25,870 --> 00:35:27,360
All right, Wilkesy!

