813
01:01:39,509 --> 01:01:41,272
Laotian Border Patrol.

814
01:01:41,344 --> 01:01:44,279
Get the recoilless rifle
right now.

815
01:01:44,347 --> 01:01:45,780
[Speaking Laotian]

816
01:01:45,849 --> 01:01:50,786
[Speaking Laotian]

817
01:01:50,887 --> 01:01:52,320
[Speaking Laotian]

818
01:01:52,389 --> 01:01:55,552
He thinks
we're opium dealers.

819
01:01:55,625 --> 01:01:57,559
They want our cargo.

820
01:01:57,627 --> 01:02:01,563
Offer him a bribe.
Anything. Stall.

821
01:02:01,631 --> 01:02:04,566
They want to inspect
our packs.

822
01:02:06,970 --> 01:02:10,133
This'll get terminal in a hurry.

823
01:02:10,206 --> 01:02:11,639
You ready,Johnson?

824
01:02:11,708 --> 01:02:12,868
Ready.

825
01:02:42,272 --> 01:02:43,261
Now!

826
01:02:59,722 --> 01:03:03,123
Scott, god damn it,
man your weapon!

827
01:03:39,329 --> 01:03:40,762
Damn it!

828
01:03:40,830 --> 01:03:43,264
Two ofthem got away!

829
01:03:43,333 --> 01:03:44,766
Colonel.

830
01:04:12,495 --> 01:04:16,295
Sir, we lost one RPG,

831
01:04:16,366 --> 01:04:17,799
six grenades,

832
01:04:17,867 --> 01:04:20,301
and a radio is damaged.

833
01:04:20,370 --> 01:04:23,305
It'll receive,
but the transmitter's shot.

834
01:04:31,381 --> 01:04:32,905
Mr.Jiang.

835
01:04:34,284 --> 01:04:35,717
We...

836
01:04:35,785 --> 01:04:37,275
come.

837
01:04:37,353 --> 01:04:39,287
We must continue on.

838
01:04:39,355 --> 01:04:43,348
No further words are
necessary, Colonel Rhodes.

839
01:04:52,335 --> 01:04:55,771
Since we don't have
night vision gear,

840
01:04:55,838 --> 01:04:59,274
we'll change to 0600
instead of 0300.

841
01:04:59,342 --> 01:05:02,277
We're able to
receive your verification

842
01:05:02,345 --> 01:05:03,778
about the P.O.W.s,

843
01:05:03,846 --> 01:05:08,283
but you'll have to assume
we've gotten the choppers.

844
01:05:08,351 --> 01:05:11,320
Wait till you
hear us coming.

845
01:05:11,387 --> 01:05:14,288
Ground team,
you're up that trail.

846
01:05:14,357 --> 01:05:17,793
Air team,
follow me down this creek.

847
01:05:19,495 --> 01:05:21,258
Well, that's it.

848
01:05:22,665 --> 01:05:24,257
It's game time.

849
01:05:26,336 --> 01:05:29,271
I've forgotten
the speech I prepared.

850
01:05:29,339 --> 01:05:32,775
There are some lines
from Julius Caesar.

851
01:05:32,842 --> 01:05:34,776
"If a man were to know

852
01:05:34,844 --> 01:05:38,211
"the end of this day's
business ere it come,

853
01:05:38,281 --> 01:05:42,240
"but it suffices
that the day will end,

854
01:05:42,318 --> 01:05:44,752
"and then
the end be known.

855
01:05:44,821 --> 01:05:46,755
"If we meet again,

856
01:05:46,823 --> 01:05:48,222
"then we'll smile.

857
01:05:48,291 --> 01:05:49,724
"And if not,

858
01:05:49,792 --> 01:05:53,228
well, then,
this parting was well made."

859
01:07:15,812 --> 01:07:19,248
It should be
right over that hill.

860
01:07:27,824 --> 01:07:29,257
Come on.

861
01:07:29,325 --> 01:07:30,758
Quietly.

862
01:07:30,827 --> 01:07:31,759
Down.

863
01:07:31,828 --> 01:07:33,261
Drop your packs.

864
01:08:12,301 --> 01:08:13,734
It looks deserted.

865
01:08:15,805 --> 01:08:18,239
You think
they moved them?

866
01:08:18,307 --> 01:08:19,740
Quite possible.

867
01:08:19,809 --> 01:08:22,744
Rice down there
has been harvested.

868
01:08:25,314 --> 01:08:27,475
I'll take a look.

869
01:08:27,583 --> 01:08:30,677
I'll look at that bridge.

870
01:09:40,289 --> 01:09:42,689
Couldn't find a way in.

871
01:09:42,758 --> 01:09:44,692
It's walled all around.

872
01:09:44,760 --> 01:09:46,193
Look at this.

873
01:09:46,262 --> 01:09:47,194
What?

874
01:09:53,769 --> 01:09:55,703
O.K., Wilkesy, I'll go.

875
01:09:55,771 --> 01:09:57,204
No, no, no.

876
01:09:57,273 --> 01:10:01,710
I'll be waiting for you
when you come out.

877
01:10:01,777 --> 01:10:03,210
O.K., Wilkesy?

878
01:10:06,816 --> 01:10:09,751
Take this.
It'll help protect you.

879
01:11:03,773 --> 01:11:05,206
Help!

880
01:11:08,044 --> 01:11:09,978
Wilkesy, you all right?

881
01:11:15,484 --> 01:11:16,917
What's wrong, man?

882
01:11:36,172 --> 01:11:38,606
It's O.K.
It's not poisonous.

883
01:11:38,674 --> 01:11:40,608
Yeah.

884
01:11:40,676 --> 01:11:43,577
That charm took care ofyou.

885
01:12:08,771 --> 01:12:10,705
I don't believe it!

886
01:12:10,773 --> 01:12:13,207
The chopper compound
isn't here.

887
01:12:13,275 --> 01:12:17,177
They must have moved
the goddamn thing.

888
01:12:17,246 --> 01:12:19,373
Give me the map.

889
01:12:26,122 --> 01:12:26,986
[Helicopter]

890
01:12:28,691 --> 01:12:30,124
Cover!

891
01:12:44,473 --> 01:12:46,065
All right, let's go.

892
01:12:46,142 --> 01:12:47,575
Let's move.

893
01:14:26,408 --> 01:14:28,000
Laotian regulars.

894
01:14:34,617 --> 01:14:36,050
Prisoners.

895
01:14:36,118 --> 01:14:39,485
They must've been
working across the river.

896
01:14:39,555 --> 01:14:42,456
That's why
we didn't see them.

897
01:15:35,077 --> 01:15:36,510
Jesus, Wilkes!

898
01:15:36,579 --> 01:15:37,944
He spotted me.

899
01:15:38,047 --> 01:15:40,481
You almost
got me spotted.

900
01:15:40,549 --> 01:15:42,483
I saw an American.

901
01:15:42,551 --> 01:15:43,984
I saw three.

902
01:15:54,530 --> 01:15:56,964
Alcatraz, this is Sing Sing.

903
01:15:57,032 --> 01:15:58,465
BMX.

904
01:15:58,534 --> 01:15:59,967
We've struck oil.

905
01:16:00,035 --> 01:16:02,799
I repeat, BMX.
We've struck oil.

906
01:16:02,872 --> 01:16:04,806
Hold it! Hold it!

907
01:16:07,543 --> 01:16:08,976
They're there!

908
01:16:09,044 --> 01:16:10,978
The P.O.W.s.
They're there!

909
01:16:11,080 --> 01:16:12,513
Jesus Christ.

910
01:16:12,581 --> 01:16:14,139
They're there!

911
01:16:20,589 --> 01:16:21,988
O.K.

912
01:16:24,560 --> 01:16:26,221
Let's find those choppers.

913
01:16:29,331 --> 01:16:31,265
It could've been Frank.

914
01:16:31,333 --> 01:16:33,267
I just don't know.

915
01:16:33,335 --> 01:16:35,769
We will know
soon enough.

916
01:16:40,009 --> 01:16:42,944
Well, I've got some
nocturnal planting to do.

917
01:16:43,012 --> 01:16:45,503
Scott, good luck.
Jiang.

918
01:16:45,581 --> 01:16:47,481
Wilkesy, let's go.

919
01:16:57,927 --> 01:17:00,862
Colonel,
we've got to move faster.

920
01:17:00,930 --> 01:17:04,366
There's a lot of jungle
to cover

921
01:17:04,433 --> 01:17:06,867
between that base and us.

922
01:17:06,936 --> 01:17:08,460
Come on.

923
01:17:32,561 --> 01:17:33,994
Where is it?

924
01:17:34,063 --> 01:17:37,931
I know it came down
in this area.

925
01:17:38,000 --> 01:17:39,991
Hurry.
It's almost dawn.

926
01:19:06,555 --> 01:19:08,455
All right.
They're asleep.

927
01:19:08,524 --> 01:19:11,960
Let's get them
before they wake up.

928
01:19:15,030 --> 01:19:17,897
Charts and Sailor,
take the barracks.

929
01:19:17,966 --> 01:19:20,457
I'll take the officers' quarters.

930
01:19:20,536 --> 01:19:23,471
Mr. Charts
must fly the helicopter.

931
01:19:23,539 --> 01:19:25,473
He cannot risk injury.

932
01:19:25,541 --> 01:19:29,477
I will go in first
with Mr. Sailor.

933
01:19:30,979 --> 01:19:31,877
Charts?

934
01:19:31,980 --> 01:19:33,470
O.K.

935
01:19:47,162 --> 01:19:50,131
They should be
on their way.

936
01:20:34,843 --> 01:20:37,573
Get out of here!
Let's go!

937
01:20:40,349 --> 01:20:41,816
Hands up!

938
01:20:46,455 --> 01:20:48,548
Charts...Charts!

939
01:20:48,624 --> 01:20:49,955
Get the gunship!

940
01:20:50,025 --> 01:20:51,458
Johnson, in the Huey!

941
01:20:51,527 --> 01:20:53,859
Hold them right here,
Sailor!

942
01:20:53,962 --> 01:20:56,897
Lai Fun, stay with Sailor!

943
01:21:11,413 --> 01:21:13,244
Battery!

944
01:21:25,694 --> 01:21:27,855
[Speaking Laotian]

945
01:21:33,001 --> 01:21:34,434
[Gunshots]

946
01:21:39,508 --> 01:21:40,941
Fucking Reds!

947
01:21:41,009 --> 01:21:42,442
I'll cover!

948
01:21:47,015 --> 01:21:49,279
Johnson's chopper
took another hit!

949
01:21:51,820 --> 01:21:53,287
Spot for me.

950
01:21:56,992 --> 01:21:58,926
I got a guy.

951
01:21:58,994 --> 01:22:01,963
200 meters,
top of the ridge,

952
01:22:02,030 --> 01:22:03,964
left of the tree.

953
01:22:05,534 --> 01:22:07,161
Right, two meters!

954
01:22:08,270 --> 01:22:09,703
Got him!

955
01:22:11,039 --> 01:22:12,301
All right!

956
01:22:14,543 --> 01:22:15,976
Baby!

957
01:22:16,044 --> 01:22:18,205
Let's go! Let's go!

958
01:22:27,522 --> 01:22:29,615
Let's go! Let's go!

959
01:22:33,028 --> 01:22:34,552
Come on, Sailor!

960
01:22:43,705 --> 01:22:45,764
Charts! Lai Fun!

961
01:23:22,544 --> 01:23:24,273
O.K., fucker!

962
01:23:32,621 --> 01:23:34,384
You're history, pal.

963
01:23:48,670 --> 01:23:50,535
Charts, are you with me?

964
01:23:50,605 --> 01:23:52,232
Right behind you.

965
01:23:52,307 --> 01:23:53,968
Johnson, are you with me?

966
01:23:54,042 --> 01:23:55,873
Right on you, Colonel!

967
01:24:16,732 --> 01:24:19,132
[Speaking Laotian]

968
01:24:47,662 --> 01:24:49,596
Shit.
Where are they?

969
01:25:01,676 --> 01:25:04,110
You cannot let them
cross the bridge!

970
01:25:04,179 --> 01:25:06,113
What if they don't show?

971
01:25:06,181 --> 01:25:07,614
They are coming.

972
01:25:07,682 --> 01:25:09,240
Don't let them
reach the bridge!

973
01:25:09,317 --> 01:25:12,115
Fire in front of them.

974
01:25:12,187 --> 01:25:13,620
Fire!

975
01:25:20,695 --> 01:25:23,630
You ain't crossing
that fucking bridge.

976
01:26:02,270 --> 01:26:03,703
It's still there!

977
01:26:03,772 --> 01:26:05,637
Goddamn caps!

978
01:26:27,329 --> 01:26:28,261
Aah!

979
01:26:46,915 --> 01:26:48,212
Hiyah!

980
01:26:48,283 --> 01:26:49,215
Hah!

981
01:27:01,596 --> 01:27:03,029
Come on, bastards!

982
01:27:03,098 --> 01:27:04,793
Come and get it!

983
01:27:07,068 --> 01:27:08,000
One!

984
01:27:10,972 --> 01:27:12,200
Two!

985
01:27:12,307 --> 01:27:14,070
Three!

986
01:27:14,142 --> 01:27:15,074
Four!

987
01:27:15,143 --> 01:27:16,075
Five!

988
01:27:16,144 --> 01:27:17,076
Six!

989
01:27:17,145 --> 01:27:18,578
A new record!

990
01:27:18,647 --> 01:27:19,579
Seven!

991
01:27:19,648 --> 01:27:21,081
Yeah! Eight!

992
01:27:21,149 --> 01:27:22,411
Unbelievable!

993
01:27:29,124 --> 01:27:31,558
We can get them out!

994
01:27:43,071 --> 01:27:44,902
Oh, my God!

995
01:28:14,903 --> 01:28:16,928
Yaah!

996
01:28:58,113 --> 01:29:00,047
Whoo! Damn it!

997
01:29:16,297 --> 01:29:18,697
Coming in on the tower.

998
01:29:23,772 --> 01:29:25,535
Son of a bitch!

999
01:29:33,148 --> 01:29:34,581
We've been hit!

1000
01:29:34,649 --> 01:29:36,082
Hold on!

1001
01:29:41,556 --> 01:29:43,490
Gun'sjammed, Colonel!

1002
01:29:46,461 --> 01:29:48,827
I'll take out the tower.

1003
01:29:48,897 --> 01:29:50,592
O.K., boss!

1004
01:30:02,110 --> 01:30:04,044
We're going to hit heavy!

1005
01:30:16,758 --> 01:30:18,020
Colonel!

1006
01:30:18,093 --> 01:30:20,425
Wilkes, give me a hand.

1007
01:30:20,495 --> 01:30:22,087
Jesus Christ!

1008
01:30:22,163 --> 01:30:24,028
Are you all right?

1009
01:30:24,099 --> 01:30:25,031
Yeah.

1010
01:30:27,669 --> 01:30:29,534
We saw four Americans,

1011
01:30:29,637 --> 01:30:31,628
one in your building!

1012
01:30:31,740 --> 01:30:33,071
Go! Go! Go!

1013
01:30:50,558 --> 01:30:51,991
Frank!

1014
01:31:04,105 --> 01:31:05,538
Come on, buddy.

1015
01:31:05,607 --> 01:31:07,472
We're going home.

1016
01:31:07,542 --> 01:31:09,009
I can't.

1017
01:31:09,110 --> 01:31:11,374
The garden.

1018
01:31:11,446 --> 01:31:13,971
We'll take it with us.

1019
01:31:14,048 --> 01:31:15,982
It's all right.

1020
01:31:16,050 --> 01:31:18,541
Come on. It's O.K.

1021
01:31:18,620 --> 01:31:20,053
Let's go.

1022
01:31:33,101 --> 01:31:35,035
Frank? Frank?

1023
01:31:43,645 --> 01:31:45,078
[Speaking Laotian]

1024
01:31:47,649 --> 01:31:49,082
It's O.K., soldier.

1025
01:31:49,150 --> 01:31:50,583
It's all right.

1026
01:31:50,652 --> 01:31:52,085
It's O.K.

1027
01:31:55,924 --> 01:31:56,856
No!

1028
01:31:56,925 --> 01:31:58,859
Come on, let's go.

1029
01:31:58,927 --> 01:32:00,861
Home?
Home for real?

1030
01:32:00,929 --> 01:32:02,897
Yeah! Come on!

1031
01:32:02,964 --> 01:32:05,558
Any more rounds
for the recoilless?

1032
01:32:05,633 --> 01:32:06,565
Jiang?

1033
01:32:23,685 --> 01:32:25,209
Holy shit!

1034
01:32:31,993 --> 01:32:34,587
Eeeyaahhh!

1035
01:32:53,982 --> 01:32:57,076
I'll kill you,
you motherfuckers!

1036
01:32:58,920 --> 01:33:00,353
Charts! This way!

1037
01:33:00,421 --> 01:33:02,548
Move it! Move it!

1038
01:33:02,624 --> 01:33:04,615
Come on, man!

1039
01:33:04,692 --> 01:33:07,195
Go, go, go!

1040
01:33:17,605 --> 01:33:21,041
There's no sign
of number four.

1041
01:33:21,109 --> 01:33:23,043
Where's the other
American?

1042
01:33:23,111 --> 01:33:24,544
[Speaking Laotian]

1043
01:33:24,612 --> 01:33:26,546
What's he saying?

1044
01:33:26,614 --> 01:33:28,047
In the pit.

1045
01:33:28,116 --> 01:33:29,549
Where's the pit?

1046
01:33:29,617 --> 01:33:31,551
[Speaking Laotian]

1047
01:33:31,619 --> 01:33:36,522
Give me a count of 60,
then go.

1048
01:33:36,591 --> 01:33:39,958
We can't leave anybody
behind this time.

1049
01:33:40,028 --> 01:33:43,486
Leave, or everybody
will get left behind!

1050
01:34:04,585 --> 01:34:05,847
Frank!

1051
01:34:18,099 --> 01:34:19,532
MacGregor?

1052
01:34:35,116 --> 01:34:36,981
Wilkes, cover me.

1053
01:34:57,572 --> 01:34:59,506
Run, Colonel, run!

1054
01:35:02,577 --> 01:35:03,908
Run.

1055
01:35:06,981 --> 01:35:08,505
Head for the chopper!

1056
01:35:08,583 --> 01:35:10,517
We'll be wiped out!

1057
01:35:24,599 --> 01:35:25,964
Come on!

1058
01:35:54,529 --> 01:35:56,224
God damn it!

1059
01:35:59,667 --> 01:36:00,599
Wilkes!

1060
01:36:02,070 --> 01:36:03,503
Leave it!

1061
01:36:06,307 --> 01:36:08,002
Come on! Come on!

1062
01:36:10,578 --> 01:36:12,011
Where's Sailor?

1063
01:36:12,080 --> 01:36:13,513
He's bought it!

1064
01:36:13,581 --> 01:36:15,014
He's dead!

1065
01:36:26,561 --> 01:36:28,825
Sailor! Sailor!

1066
01:36:28,930 --> 01:36:31,922
Eeeyaaah!

1067
01:36:41,542 --> 01:36:43,476
Come on, man.

1068
01:36:43,544 --> 01:36:44,977
Come on.

1069
01:36:46,547 --> 01:36:48,139
Where's Blaster?

1070
01:36:48,216 --> 01:36:49,843
God damn it!

1071
01:36:53,955 --> 01:36:55,445
Mr. Charts!

1072
01:36:55,523 --> 01:36:56,956
Mr. Scott! Come!

1073
01:36:57,024 --> 01:36:57,956
Come quickly!

1074
01:36:58,025 --> 01:36:59,390
This way!

1075
01:36:59,460 --> 01:37:00,484
Charts, come on!

1076
01:37:00,561 --> 01:37:01,994
We got to hustle!

1077
01:37:02,096 --> 01:37:02,994
Come on!

1078
01:37:19,313 --> 01:37:21,247
[Gunfire]

1079
01:37:38,032 --> 01:37:41,468
Mayday! Mayday!
American M.I.A.s on board!

1080
01:37:43,037 --> 01:37:44,470
Mayday! Mayday!

1081
01:37:44,539 --> 01:37:48,168
Chartsy, give me
a hand up here.

1082
01:37:51,045 --> 01:37:52,478
Mayday! Mayday!

1083
01:37:52,547 --> 01:37:54,708
American M.I.A.s
on board!

1084
01:38:23,578 --> 01:38:25,512
It's really good...

1085
01:38:25,580 --> 01:38:27,343
to see you.

1086
01:38:33,087 --> 01:38:34,486
Frank...

1087
01:38:37,491 --> 01:38:39,425
He got sick.

1088
01:38:40,728 --> 01:38:42,161
So sick.

1089
01:38:43,531 --> 01:38:45,965
I tried to help him.

1090
01:38:48,035 --> 01:38:50,094
He died.

1091
01:39:00,047 --> 01:39:02,914
He saved my life
